--- SCENARIO: herson draft resolves ranked picks submitted over DM ---
# Herson is a ranked secret draft. Each player DMs four ranked picks as free text (no /pick). With no
# clashes the bot resolves immediately; picks stay hidden until then and are revealed in the status
# message. The group stream only ever holds the three milestone replies (start / all-in / resolved).

--- CHAT ---
alice: /lobby herson
bob: /register
ambotorix: <status *Status: waiting*Draft: herson*Players (2):*>

--- DM (alice) ---
alice: /leaders                  # open a private chat so the bot can DM the pick prompt
ambotorix: <button "{leader}">
--- DM (bob) ---
bob: /leaders
ambotorix: <button "{leader}">

--- CHAT ---
alice: /start
ambotorix: <status *Status: drafting*Submissions: 0/2 in*>
ambotorix: @alice* @bob* <backlink>     # draft-start ping, replying to the status message
ambotorix:                              # nothing else in the group yet

--- DM (alice) ---
ambotorix: *Herson draft*               # the pick prompt
alice: 1. lincoln 2. curtin 3. montezuma 4. hammurabi
ambotorix: *Picks recorded*

--- CHAT ---
ambotorix: <status *Submissions: 1/2 in*>
ambotorix:                              # still just the start ping in the stream

--- DM (bob) ---
ambotorix: *Herson draft*
bob: 1. pedro 2. basil 3. theodora 4. laurier
ambotorix: *Picks recorded*

--- CHAT ---
ambotorix: 📥 All picks are in* <backlink>
ambotorix: 🎉 Draft resolved!* <backlink>
ambotorix: <status *Status: done*Picks:*@{player} → {leader}*@{player} → {leader}*>
ambotorix:                              # group stream held exactly the three milestones
